1. Setup:
	1. Install node
	2. Install browser-sync: npm install -g browser-sync
3. Use browser sync: browser-sync start --server --directory --files "*"
	1.Issue with port 3000 for browser-sync. Solution: https://github.com/docker/for-win/issues/3171
4. Websites:
	1. Share javascript code with others: https://jsfiddle.net
	2. https://codepen.io
	3. https://css-tricks.com